			<change xml:lang="EN">
				<p sameAs="title">Business letter written by Miguel Correia Cardoso de Leão Soares to Valério Máximo da Costa, administrator of Santa Marta Chapel, in Lisbon.</p>
				<p sameAs="summary"></p>
				<p sameAs="settingDesc">Miguel Correia Cardoso de Leão Soares was accused of falsifying the signature of the judge from Setúbal. He was also an humbug, pretending to be the registrar in the Setúbal court. Under this false identity, he wrote to Valério Máximo da Costa, administrator of Santa Marta Chapel, asking that he paid different amounts of money to his attorney.</p>
				<p sameAs="text">Illustrious Mr. Valério Máximo.</p></change>
		</revisionDesc>
